#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1285
msgid "• Local proxy"
msgstr "• Proxy local"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1305
msgid ""
"If you are on a corporate or university network, you might need to configure "
"a local proxy."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda berada di jaringan perusahaan atau universitas, Anda mungkin perlu "
"mengonfigurasi proxy lokal."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1335
msgid "Configure a Local _Proxy"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan Proksi Lokal _"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1374
msgid "• Tor bridge"
msgstr "• Bridge Tor"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1394
msgid ""
"Tor bridges are secret Tor relays. Use a bridge as your first Tor relay if "
"connections to Tor are blocked, for example in some countries, by some "
"public networks, or by some parental controls."
msgstr ""
"Bridge Tor adalah relay Tor rahasia. Gunakan bridge sebagai relay Tor "
"pertama Anda jika koneksi ke Tor diblokir, misalnya di beberapa negara, oleh "
"beberapa jaringan publik, atau oleh beberapa kontrol orang tua."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1410
msgid "Configure a Tor _Bridge"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan _Bridge Tor"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1449
msgid ""
"<a href=\"doc/anonymous_internet/tor/troubleshoot\">Troubleshooting "
"connecting to Tor</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"doc/anonymous_internet/tor/troubleshoot\">Pemecahan masalah "
"menyambung ke Tor</a>"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1494
#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1902
msgid ""
"Everything you do on the Internet from Tails goes through the Tor network."
msgstr "Semua yang Anda lakukan di Internet dari Tails melewati jaringan Tor."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1508
#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1917
msgid ""
"Tor encrypts and anonymizes your connection by passing it through 3 relays.\n"
"Tor relays are servers operated by different organizations and volunteers "
"around the world."
msgstr ""
"Tor mengenkripsi dan menganonimkan koneksi Anda dengan melewatkannya melalui "
"3 relai.\n"
"Relay Tor adalah server yang dioperasikan oleh berbagai organisasi dan "
"sukarelawan di seluruh dunia."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1544
msgid "<b>Connect to Tor _automatically</b>"
msgstr "<b>Hubungkan ke Tor secara _otomatis</b>"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1594
msgid ""
"We recommend connecting to Tor automatically if you are on a public Wi-Fi "
"network or if many people in your country use Tor to circumvent censorship."
msgstr ""
"Kami menyarankan untuk menghubungkan ke Tor secara otomatis jika Anda berada "
"di jaringan Wi-Fi publik atau jika banyak orang di negara Anda menggunakan "
"Tor untuk menghindari penyensoran."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1612
msgid ""
"Tails will try different ways of connecting to Tor until it succeeds.\n"
"\n"
"Someone monitoring your Internet connection could identify these attempts as "
"coming from a Tails user."
msgstr ""
"Tails akan mencoba berbagai cara untuk menghubungkan ke Tor sampai "
"berhasil.\n"
"\n"
"Seseorang yang memantau koneksi Internet Anda dapat mengidentifikasi upaya "
"ini berasal dari pengguna Tails."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1646
msgid "Configure a Tor _bridge"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan _bridge Tor"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1692
msgid ""
"Tor bridges are secret Tor relays. Use a bridge as your first Tor relay if "
"connections to Tor are blocked, for example in some countries, by some "
"public networks, or by some parental controls.\n"
"\n"
"Choose this option if you already know that you need a bridge. Otherwise, "
"Tails will autodetect whether you need a bridge to connect to Tor from your "
"local network."
msgstr ""
"Jembatan Tor adalah relay Tor yang rahasia. Gunakan bridge sebagai relai Tor "
"pertama Anda jika koneksi ke Tor diblokir, misalnya di beberapa negara, oleh "
"beberapa jaringan publik, atau oleh kontrol orang tua.\n"
"\n"
"Pilih opsi ini jika Anda sudah tahu bahwa Anda membutuhkan bridge. Jika "
"tidak, Tails akan otomatis mendeteksi apakah Anda memerlukan bridge untuk "
"terhubung ke Tor dari jaringan lokal Anda."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1734
msgid "<b>_Hide to my local network that I'm connecting to Tor</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>_Sembunyikan dari jaringan lokal saya bahwa saya sedang terhubung ke Tor</"
"b>"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1784
msgid ""
"You might need to go unnoticed if using Tor could look suspicious to someone "
"who monitors your Internet connection."
msgstr ""
"Anda mungkin perlu tidak terdeteksi jika penggunaan Tor dapat terlihat "
"mencurigakan bagi seseorang yang memantau koneksi Internet Anda."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1802
msgid ""
"Tails will only connect to Tor after you configured a Tor bridge. Bridges "
"are secret Tor relays that hide that you are connecting to Tor.\n"
"\n"
"Our team is doing its best to help you connect to Tor using the most "
"discreet types of Tor bridges.\n"
"\n"
"You will have to do extra configuration if you don't know any Tor bridges "
"yet, if you connect from a public Wi-Fi network, or if you are in the "
"Eastern Hemisphere."
msgstr ""
"Tails hanya akan terhubung ke Tor setelah Anda mengonfigurasi bridge Tor. "
"bridge adalah relai Tor rahasia yang menyembunyikan bahwa Anda terhubung ke "
"Tor.\n"
"\n"
"Tim kami melakukan yang terbaik untuk membantu Anda terhubung ke Tor "
"menggunakan jenis bridge Tor yang paling berbeda.\n"
"\n"
"Anda harus melakukan konfigurasi tambahan jika Anda belum mengetahui bridge "
"Tor, jika Anda terhubung dari jaringan Wi-Fi publik, atau jika Anda berada "
"di Belahan Bumi Timur."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1847
msgid ""
"<a href=\"doc/anonymous_internet/tor\">Learn more about how Tails connects "
"to Tor</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"doc/anonymous_internet/tor\">Pelajari lebih lanjut tentang "
"bagaimana Tails terhubung ke Tor</a>"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1937
msgid "No Wi-Fi hardware detected"
msgstr "Tidak terdeteksi perangkat keras Wi-Fi"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1955
msgid ""
"Tails couldn't find any Wi-Fi interface on your computer. If your computer "
"has a Wi-Fi interface, it might not work on Tails.\n"
"\n"
"To connect to the Internet you can try to:\n"
"\n"
" • Use an Ethernet cable instead of Wi-Fi. Wired interfaces work much more "
"reliably than Wi-Fi in Tails.\n"
" • Use USB tethering to share the Wi-Fi or mobile data connection of your "
"phone using a cable.\n"
" • Buy a USB Wi-Fi adapter that works in Tails.\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"Tails tidak dapat menemukan antarmuka Wi-Fi apa pun di komputer Anda. Jika "
"komputer Anda memiliki antarmuka Wi-Fi, mungkin tidak berfungsi di Tails.\n"
"\n"
"Untuk terhubung ke Internet Anda dapat mencoba:\n"
"\n"
" • Gunakan kabel Ethernet sebagai pengganti Wi-Fi. Antarmuka kabel bekerja "
"jauh lebih andal daripada Wi-Fi di Tails.\n"
" • Gunakan tethering USB untuk berbagi koneksi Wi-Fi atau data seluler "
"ponsel Anda menggunakan kabel.\n"
" • Beli adaptor Wi-Fi USB yang berfungsi di Tails.\n"
"                "

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:1979
msgid ""
"\n"
"<a href=\"doc/anonymous_internet/no-wifi\">\n"
"Learn more about troubleshooting Wi-Fi not working.\n"
"</a>\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<a href=\"doc/anonymous_internet/no-wifi\">\n"
"Pelajari lebih lanjut tentang pemecahan masalah Wi-Fi yang tidak berfungsi.\n"
"</a>\n"
"                "

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:2007
msgid "Connect to a local network"
msgstr "Hubungkan ke jaringan lokal"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/tca/main.ui.in:2024
msgid ""
"You are not connected to a local network yet. To be able to connect to the "
"Tor network, you first need to connect to a Wi-Fi, wired, or mobile network."
msgstr ""
"Anda belum terhubung ke jaringan lokal. Agar dapat terhubung ke jaringan "
"Tor, Anda terlebih dahulu harus terhubung ke jaringan Wi-Fi, kabel, atau "
"seluler."

